name: Noden Generative
description:
Introducing the major players within the ranks of Generatives and Disruptives at Gormenghast.

Noden Generative – Noden is one of a new generation coming through Generative families. An extract of the Otoris coupling, Noden has the gift (or the curse) of knowing all timelines forward and back simultaneously.

It’s likely that this trait would collapse the mind of any not of the Otoris lineage, so Noden is doing extremely well to contain the possible madness. It helps in knowing the future timelines that she’s aware she isn’t driven insane; but also she knows of her fate – she knows she’s going to be kidnapped and betrayed by one of her kin.

Unfortunately it is at this point in her future that all else is hidden by temporal fog and she cannot see why. Knowing that this is to happen whilst also knowing that it can’t be stopped because it has already happened can sometimes be a struggle for such a young mind.

So why is one so young such a major player? Because she’s an Oracle; and Oracles are extremely rare.

PNG 4800 x 4800 || December 12th 2021 || Dark Art digital painting – expanding the Gormenghast origin universe
